1
00:00:48,214 --> 00:00:54,847
愤怒的公牛

2
00:02:53,105 --> 00:02:55,505
纽约市 1964年

3
00:02:55,608 --> 00:02:57,235
夜访杰克拉莫塔

4
00:02:57,343 --> 00:02:59,106
我记得那些欢呼声
I remember those cheers,

5
00:02:59,712 --> 00:03:01,304
至今仍在耳边回响
they still ring in my ears,

6
00:03:01,414 --> 00:03:04,247
多年来仍不时想到它们
and for years they remain in my thoughts,

7
00:03:04,350 --> 00:03:05,681
有一天晚上
'cause one night,

8
00:03:05,785 --> 00:03:07,844
我脱掉我的外袍,结果呢?
I took off my robe, and what'd I do?

9
00:03:07,954 --> 00:03:10,081
我忘了穿上短裤
I forgot to wear shorts.

10
00:03:11,958 --> 00:03:15,758
我记得每一次跌倒 每一个勾拳和直拳
I recall every fall, every hook, every jab,

11
00:03:16,295 --> 00:03:19,025
还有最糟的减肥方法
the worst way a guy can get rid of his flab,

12
00:03:19,131 --> 00:03:21,429
你知道我的人生并不平淡
as you know, my life wasn't drab.

13
00:03:22,802 --> 00:03:24,269
不过我宁愿...
Though I'd much...

14
00:03:25,304 --> 00:03:27,602
我宁愿听你们欢呼...
Though I'd rather hear you cheer when you delve...

15
00:03:27,707 --> 00:03:30,676
我宁愿你们是因为 听我演莎士比亚而欢呼...
Though I'd rather hear you cheer when I delve into Shakespeare...

16
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:33,540
“马儿!马儿! 一匹马毁了我的王国!”
"A horse! A horse! My kingdom for a horse!"

17
00:03:33,646 --> 00:03:35,614
我有六个月没赢了
I haven't had a winner in six months.

18
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:43,254
虽然我不是奥立维,我宁愿...
And though I'm no Olivier, I would much rather...

19
00:03:45,324 --> 00:03:47,952
虽然我不是奥立维 如果他跟罗宾森对打的话
And though I'm no Olivier, if he fought Sugar Ray,

20
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:50,893
他会说重点不是比赛,而是娱乐
he would say that the thing ain't the ring, it's the play.

21
00:03:50,997 --> 00:03:54,398
让我这只公牛 有个可以发威的舞台吧
So, give me a stage where this bull here can rage,

22
00:03:54,500 --> 00:03:57,469
虽然我可以打斗,我宁愿吟诵
and though I can fight, I'd much rather recite.

23
00:03:58,604 --> 00:04:00,128
那才是娱乐
That's entertainment.

24
00:04:01,974 --> 00:04:05,375
杰克拉莫塔 1964年

25
00:04:05,745 --> 00:04:07,212
-杰克拉莫塔,1941年 -那才是娱乐
That's entertainment.

26
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,907
杰克拉莫塔和吉米里维
Jake La Motta and Jimmy Reeves

27
00:04:09,015 --> 00:04:10,482
在克利夫兰体育场
in the Cleveland Arena.

28
00:04:10,583 --> 00:04:13,609
拉莫塔还没被击倒 但是得分落后很多
La Motta is undefeated, but he's well behind on points.

29
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:16,813
布朗克斯公牛在这一局挨了不少拳
The Bronx Bull has taken a lot of punishment in this bout.

30
00:04:16,923 --> 00:04:20,188
杰克的左眼受伤 吉米里维略胜...
Jake is cut around the left eye. Jimmy Reeves has outboxed him...

31
00:04:20,293 --> 00:04:23,592
杰克,告诉我 我们它妈的干嘛跑来克利夫兰
Jack, tell me, why the fuck do we have to come to Cleveland for you

32
00:04:23,696 --> 00:04:24,822
看你被小打败?
to get beaten by a mulignane?

33
00:04:24,931 --> 00:04:26,831
拜托,它妈的振作起来吧
Come on, do the fuckin' right thing.

34
00:04:26,933 --> 00:04:29,094
他吃定你了,你得分落后
He's got you by the balls, you're outpointed.

35
00:04:29,201 --> 00:04:31,829
你要在第十局领先 你得把他打倒在地
You're comin' up for the tenth, you're gonna have to knock him out.

36
00:04:31,938 --> 00:04:34,099
我要你咬他,踢他,不择手段
I want you to bite him, kick him, do anything you gotta do.

37
00:04:34,206 --> 00:04:36,037
没人会看到,你知道怎么做
Nobody's lookin', you know what to do.

38
00:04:36,142 --> 00:04:38,110
和在家乡一样...痛扁那些王八蛋
Just like home... all over the fuckin' moolies.

39
00:04:38,210 --> 00:04:41,008
把那混蛋打倒 听懂没?把他打倒
Knock the motherfucker out. You understand? Knock him out.

40
00:04:41,113 --> 00:04:43,377
你想上场吗? 你想上场去打吗?
Hey, you wanna go in there? You wanna go in and do it?

41
00:04:47,420 --> 00:04:48,546
救命!
Help!

42
00:04:50,323 --> 00:04:52,120
咱们上场去把他打倒吧
We need a knockout, let's go get a knockout,

43
00:04:52,224 --> 00:04:53,191
上场去吧
that's where it's at.

44
00:04:53,292 --> 00:04:55,988
第十局,最后一局 祝你们好运
Tenth and final round. Good luck to you both.

45
00:04:56,095 --> 00:04:58,120
拉莫塔位居下风
La Motta fighting out of a halfcrouch.

46
00:04:58,230 --> 00:05:00,221
里维面对难缠的对手
Reeves is up against a tough fighter,

47
00:05:00,333 --> 00:05:02,301
一个绝不打退堂鼓的人
a man who doesn't know how to back up.

48
00:05:02,401 --> 00:05:05,962
拉莫塔持续进攻 说时迟哪时快
La Motta continues to bore in, out of the bob and weave,

49
00:05:06,072 --> 00:05:08,563
左勾拳打到下巴 里维倒地了!
hooks a left hand to the jaw, and Reeves is down!

50
00:05:10,276 --> 00:05:12,574
观众在为杰克加油
The crowd is urging Jake on.

51
00:05:13,346 --> 00:05:16,577
裁判在为里维计时 他得快爬起来
The referee is tolling over Reeves. He's got to get up.

52
00:05:16,682 --> 00:05:19,310
拉莫塔再度进攻 里维的右拳没打中
La Motta comes at him once again, Reeves misses a right,

53
00:05:19,418 --> 00:05:22,319
吃了两记左拳 一记重重的左拳打中下巴
takes a left, and another left, a hard left hand to the jaw,

54
00:05:22,421 --> 00:05:24,889
里维二度倒地
and Reeves is down for the second time.

55
00:05:24,957 --> 00:05:28,188
意志坚定的杰克拉莫塔在第十局
A determined Jake La Motta is making a great comeback

56
00:05:28,294 --> 00:05:29,761
漂亮地抢回优势
here in the tenth round.

57
00:05:31,163 --> 00:05:33,927
里维又爬起来,拉莫塔进攻
Reeves is up again, La Motta comes at him.

58
00:05:34,033 --> 00:05:37,196
下巴一记左勾拳 又一记左拳,右拳打中身体
Aleft hook to the jaw, another left, and a right to the body.

59
00:05:37,303 --> 00:05:39,931
三个左拳打中上半身 下巴一记勾拳
Three more lefts to the midsection, a hook on the jaw,

60
00:05:40,039 --> 00:05:43,031
头部又两记左拳 下巴一记右拳又一记左拳
two more lefts to the head, a right and a left to the jaw.

61
00:05:43,142 --> 00:05:45,133
里维第三度倒地
Reeves goes down for the third time,

62
00:05:45,244 --> 00:05:47,508
裁判把拉莫塔拉走
and the referee is pulling La Motta away.

63
00:05:47,613 --> 00:05:49,604
二...三...
Two... three...

64
00:05:49,715 --> 00:05:51,205
四...五...
four... five...

65
00:05:51,317 --> 00:05:53,808
-裁判在为里维计时 -六...七...
- The referee is counting over Reeves, - six... seven...

66
00:05:53,919 --> 00:05:55,944
-但是时间不多了 -八...九...
- but time is running out... - eight... nine...

67
00:05:56,055 --> 00:05:57,522
铃响了
...and there is the bell.

68
00:05:58,257 --> 00:06:01,715
动弹不得的里维被铃声解救
He can't walk, but Reeves has been saved by the bell.

69
00:06:01,827 --> 00:06:03,727
但拉莫塔会不会动作慢了点?
But did La Motta do it soon enough?

70
00:06:03,829 --> 00:06:05,296
杰克,杰克,过来
Jack, Jack, come here.

71
00:06:05,364 --> 00:06:08,231
这样不行 这里是俄亥俄,不是纽约!
It's no good. This is Ohio, not New York!

72
00:06:08,334 --> 00:06:10,666
-你等得太久了! -那个笨蛋!
- You waited too long! - That dumb bastard!

73
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:13,637
把袍子穿好 把我的袍子穿好!
Put the robe on right, huh? Put my robe on right!

74
00:06:14,874 --> 00:06:16,899
各位女士先生...
Ladies and gentlemen...

75
00:06:18,277 --> 00:06:22,441
根据俄亥俄拳击委员会的规定
...under the rules of the Ohio Boxing Commission,

76
00:06:23,215 --> 00:06:25,183
一致决定
after ten rounds,

77
00:06:25,851 --> 00:06:29,844
这十局比赛的获胜者是
the winner, by unanimous decision,

78
00:06:31,023 --> 00:06:33,821
-吉米里维! -精彩的杰克拉莫塔
- Jimmy Reeves! - The colorful Jake La Motta,

79
00:06:33,926 --> 00:06:36,952
布朗克斯公牛输了第一场比赛
the Bronx Bull, has lost his first fight.

80
00:06:40,966 --> 00:06:44,197
是杰克赢了比赛! 拜托,杰克赢了比赛!
That's Jake's fight! Come on, that's Jake's fight!

81
00:06:44,303 --> 00:06:45,668
是杰克赢了那场比赛!
Jake won that fight!

82
00:06:45,771 --> 00:06:48,706
不要走,不要下场,待在这儿
Don't leave. Don't get outta the fuckin' ring. Stay here.

83
00:06:48,808 --> 00:06:51,641
你赢了...让他先走 你给我留下来
You won... let him go first. Stay in, I'm tellin' you.

84
00:06:51,744 --> 00:06:54,440
拉莫塔在比赛中打倒里维七次
La Motta floored Reeves seven times in the fight,

85
00:06:54,547 --> 00:06:56,845
但是拉莫塔居然输了比赛
but La Motta still lost the fight.

86
00:07:01,987 --> 00:07:03,887
杰克!杰克!杰克!杰克!
Jake! Jake! Jake! Jake!

87
00:07:20,039 --> 00:07:21,063
救命啊!
Help!

88
00:07:43,729 --> 00:07:44,855
纽约市布朗克斯区 1941年

89
00:07:44,964 --> 00:07:47,455
...他躺在地上 他们把他抬走,他不醒人事
...on his fuckin' back, they pick up his arm, he's dead.

90
00:07:47,566 --> 00:07:50,057
他们说他赢了比赛,观众抓狂了
They tell him he won the fight. People went crazy.

91
00:07:50,169 --> 00:07:53,104
如果有汤米照应 就不会发生那种鸟事
That shit woulda never happened if Tommy was there takin' care of it.

92
00:07:53,205 --> 00:07:56,436
他在纽约比赛 要听汤米的话才能打进冠军赛
He's gotta be with Tommy to fight in New York, to get a title shot.

93
00:07:56,542 --> 00:07:58,476
你哥哥会变成酒鬼
He's gonna wind up punch-drunk, your brother.

94
00:07:58,577 --> 00:07:59,805
-我知道 -你知道
- I know. - You know.

95
00:07:59,945 --> 00:08:03,403
你得让他明白这样对大家都好
You gotta make him understand it's the best thing for everybody involved.

96
00:08:03,482 --> 00:08:05,382
-我说我知道 -你知道
- I said I know. - You know,

97
00:08:05,484 --> 00:08:08,112
可是你得让他知道,让他明白
but you gotta make him know, make him understand it.

98
00:08:08,220 --> 00:08:09,551
老天,你要不要住口?
Jesus Christ, you wanna stop?

99
00:08:09,655 --> 00:08:11,555
你何时才会它妈的停止?
When the fuck you gonna stop with that stuff?

100
00:08:11,657 --> 00:08:13,488
我跟你说过我都明白
I told ya, I understand everything.

101
00:08:13,592 --> 00:08:15,560
他只会为自己着想
He just wants to do things for himself.

102
00:08:15,661 --> 00:08:17,561
-听不懂吗? -那是因为他是
- Hard to understand? - It's because he's got a head

103
00:08:17,663 --> 00:08:19,563
-死脑筋 -你很好笑耶
- like concrete. - You make me laugh.

104
00:08:19,665 --> 00:08:21,758
你以为很容易? 你怎么不去跟他说?
You think it's easy? Why don't you talk to him?

105
00:08:21,867 --> 00:08:23,664
-你知道要说什么 -你知道我没办法和他说话
- You know what to say. - You know I can't talk to him.

106
00:08:23,769 --> 00:08:25,669
-为什么不行? -因为他不喜欢我
- Why can't you talk to him? - 'Cause he don't like me.

107
00:08:25,771 --> 00:08:27,432
没人喜欢你,你应该习惯了
Nobody likes you, you oughta be used to it.

108
00:08:29,375 --> 00:08:30,501
大家知道
They knew.

109
00:08:31,610 --> 00:08:33,077
大家知道谁赢了
They knew who was the boss.

110
00:08:36,882 --> 00:08:39,510
裁判不知道 谁知道这些人是怎么回事?
The judges didn't know. Who knows what happened with them?

111
00:08:40,052 --> 00:08:41,417
观众知道
The people knew.

112
00:08:42,521 --> 00:08:45,854
你不相信我 你以为我在那儿胡搞吗?
You don't believe me, you thought I was over there foolin' around, huh?

113
00:08:45,958 --> 00:08:48,927
你以为我在胡搞对不对? 告诉我实话
You thought I was foolin' around, didn't ya? Tell me the truth.

114
00:08:49,028 --> 00:08:50,962
我可不是胡搞瞎搞
I ain't doin' no foolin' around.

115
00:08:51,063 --> 00:08:54,226
-是你这么想 -是又怎么样?
- That's in your mind. - Yeah, so what?

116
00:08:54,333 --> 00:08:57,791
等我戴上冠军腰带 我才会开始胡搞
That championship belt on me, that's when I fool around.

117
00:09:00,806 --> 00:09:01,864
熟了没?
Is it done?

118
00:09:02,508 --> 00:09:04,339
还没熟
No, it's not done.

119
00:09:04,443 --> 00:09:07,139
不要煎太老 煎太老就不好吃了
Don't overcook it. You overcook it, it's no good.

120
00:09:08,247 --> 00:09:10,374
它就失去意义了
It defeats its own purpose.

121
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:17,214
你在做什么? 我说了不要煎太老
What are you doin'? I just said don't overcook it.

122
00:09:17,323 --> 00:09:19,382
你把它煎老了,拿过来呀
You're overcookin' it, bring it over.

123
00:09:19,491 --> 00:09:21,550
-你要你的牛排吗? -拿过来呀
- You want your steak? - Bring it over.

124
00:09:22,261 --> 00:09:23,785
拿过来!
Bring it over!

125
00:09:23,896 --> 00:09:26,990
快变成木炭了!拿过来!
It's like a piece of charcoal! Bring it over here!

126
00:09:27,099 --> 00:09:29,499
-你要你的牛排? -对,现在就要!
- You want your steak? - Yeah, right now!

127
00:09:29,602 --> 00:09:32,264
好,你的臭牛排
Good. There's your stupid steak.

128
00:09:32,371 --> 00:09:34,839
-等不及把它煎熟是吧? -对,我等不及了
- Can't wait for it to be done? - No, I can't wait.

129
00:09:34,940 --> 00:09:36,931
好,可以了吗?高兴了吗?
Good. Okay? Happy?

130
00:09:37,042 --> 00:09:38,600
-高兴了吗? -我只要这个
- Happy? - That's all I want.

131
00:09:38,711 --> 00:09:40,576
拿去,没有了,都拿去
That's... there, no, more. There.

132
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:45,277
你为了牛排跟我吵? 你为了牛排跟我吵?
Botherin' me about a steak, huh? You're botherin' me about a steak?!

133
00:09:45,384 --> 00:09:47,352
我同意,他应该听汤米的
I agree with you. He should be with Tommy.

134
00:09:47,453 --> 00:09:50,286
他如果心情好,我会跟他说 不然你要我怎么样?
If he's in a good mood, I'll talk to him. What the fuck you want me to do?

135
00:09:50,389 --> 00:09:52,186
汤米每天都要我来找你
Tommy tells me every day to talk to you

136
00:09:52,291 --> 00:09:53,781
去跟杰克谈,解决这件事
and speak to Jake to straighten this thing out,

137
00:09:53,893 --> 00:09:55,417
到头来我会两面不是人
I'm gonna wind up in the middle.

138
00:09:55,527 --> 00:09:56,824
你两面不是人?我是他弟弟
You're in the middle? I'm his brother.

139
00:09:56,929 --> 00:09:59,124
-他把我搞疯了 -你是他弟弟
- He's got me fuckin' nuts. - You're his brother.

140
00:09:59,231 --> 00:10:01,597
如果你不能跟他谈,谁能跟他谈?
If you can't talk to him, who's gonna talk to him?

141
00:10:03,302 --> 00:10:05,202
-我会跟他谈 -你尽力就好
- I'll talk to him. - Do what you can, that's all.

142
00:10:05,304 --> 00:10:07,033
-我只求这么多 -明天见
- That's all I'm askin' you. - I'll see you tomorrow.

143
00:10:07,139 --> 00:10:09,437
-让我上去 -好吗?你会在哪儿?
- Let me go up. - All right? Where you gonna be?

144
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:11,532
我会在体育馆或其它的老地方
I'll be at the gym or the other joint, one of the two.

145
00:10:11,644 --> 00:10:13,544
-我会去体育馆找你 -好,沙维?
- I'll catch you by the gym. - All right. Sal?

146
00:10:13,646 --> 00:10:15,614
-怎么? -去死吧
Yeah?

147
00:10:17,416 --> 00:10:19,543
再抱怨啊,我要听听
Complain some more, I wanna hear.

148
00:10:19,652 --> 00:10:22,553
-抱怨?这是胡萝卜吗? -没错
- Complain? You call those carrots? - That's right.

149
00:10:22,655 --> 00:10:24,486
-这算是食物吗? -你吃啦,你有没有吃?
- You call that food? - You ate 'em. Did you eat them?

150
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:26,285
这算是食物吗?我没有选择啊!
You call that food? I got no choice!

151
00:10:26,392 --> 00:10:28,087
-我受不了你了! -我没有选择啊!
- I'm sick of you already! - I got no choice!

152
00:10:28,193 --> 00:10:32,061
-我不敢相信! -我没有选择!
- I can't believe you! - I got no choice!

153
00:10:32,164 --> 00:10:34,724
你没有选择?离我远一点!
You got no choice? Get away from me!

154
00:10:34,833 --> 00:10:37,131
-拜托你! -给我进来,给我进来!
- Please! - Get in there. Get in there!

155
00:10:37,236 --> 00:10:39,830
不要碰我,离我远一点!
Get your hands off me, get away from me!

156
00:10:39,939 --> 00:10:41,839
它妈的!我受够你了!
Fuck! I'm sick of you!

157
00:10:41,941 --> 00:10:43,966
在搞什么,你们是畜牲吗?
