01:13:17,259 --> 01:13:19,819
只要他不死掉 你可以进入冠军赛
You're gonna get your shot, as long as he don't die.

1124
01:13:21,029 --> 01:13:23,020
-只要谁不死? -汤米
- As long as who don't die? - Tommy.

1125
01:13:23,131 --> 01:13:24,689
你在说什么?
What are you talkin' about?

1126
01:13:24,800 --> 01:13:26,700
换句话说,汤米不会忘了你
In other words, Tommy ain't gonna forget ya,

1127
01:13:26,802 --> 01:13:28,030
只要他不死,你就能参赛
you're gonna get your shot if he don't die.

1128
01:13:28,136 --> 01:13:30,195
-要保住这家伙的命 -他生病了吗?
- Gotta make sure the guy stays alive. - He got a disease or somethin'?

1129
01:13:30,305 --> 01:13:32,205
没有,我只是说说,开玩笑
No, I'm just sayin', I'm kiddin', like.

1130
01:13:32,307 --> 01:13:34,070
他怎么了?他有什么毛病吗?
What's wrong with him? Is somethin' wrong with him?

1131
01:13:34,176 --> 01:13:36,110
他没有毛病 我是说你一定能打进去
There ain't nothin' wrong with him, that's the only way you wouldn't get it

1132
01:13:36,211 --> 01:13:39,112
-除非他死了,不然... -你干嘛说这种话?
- is if he dies, he won't be able to... - What are you talkin' like that for?

1133
01:13:39,214 --> 01:13:40,545
两年后 底特律1949年6月15日

1134
01:13:40,916 --> 01:13:43,510
中量级冠军 马赛瑟顿

1135
01:13:43,618 --> 01:13:46,212
挑战者 杰克拉莫塔

1136
01:13:46,321 --> 01:13:47,788
欢迎光临

1137
01:13:47,889 --> 01:13:49,379
你要我怎样?这是户外体育场
What do you want me to do? It's an outdoor arena.

1138
01:13:49,491 --> 01:13:52,289
你想在雨中比赛吗? 这是体育场
What do you wanna do, fight in the rain? It's a stadium.

1139
01:13:52,394 --> 01:13:53,986
你都等这么久了 你可以再等一下
You waited this long, you can wait longer.

1140
01:13:54,663 --> 01:13:57,131
你想等二十四小时吗? 我可不想等二十四小时
You wanna wait 24 hours? I don't wanna wait no 24 hours.

1141
01:13:57,232 --> 01:14:00,292
我也不想 可是我们不得不等,喂?
I don't either, but we gotta, so we'll wait. Hello?

1142
01:14:01,002 --> 01:14:04,062
-你们可不可以住嘴? -不要和他们讲电话
- You guys wanna stop now? - Get off the phone with them.

1143
01:14:04,172 --> 01:14:05,730
你干嘛让他们称心如意?
Why do you give them the satisfaction?

1144
01:14:05,841 --> 01:14:08,139
-别和他们讲电话了! -他不想和任何人说话
- Get off the phone with them! - He don't wanna talk to nobody.

1145
01:14:08,243 --> 01:14:10,404
要跟你讲几次才行? 你没听到他在骂吗?
How many times do we have to tell ya? You hear him yellin'?

1146
01:14:10,512 --> 01:14:13,072
这里已经够混乱了 拜托别再打来了
There's enough confusion up here. Please, don't call.

1147
01:14:13,181 --> 01:14:16,480
无可奉告,对 谢谢,再见!
No comment. Right. Thank you. Bye!

1148
01:14:16,585 --> 01:14:18,576
真讨厌,真不敢相信
Pains in the asses, I don't believe them.

1149
01:14:18,687 --> 01:14:21,315
你干嘛让他们称心如意? 干嘛不挂他们电话?
Why do you give them the satisfaction? Why don't you just hang up on 'em?

1150
01:14:21,423 --> 01:14:23,323
-挂了就好 -我要吃点东西
- That's all. - I'm gonna get somethin' to eat.

1151
01:14:23,425 --> 01:14:25,552
-你想吃什么? -我不想吃
- What do you want to eat? - I don't want nothin'.

1152
01:14:26,094 --> 01:14:27,220
我不想吃
I don't want nothin'.

1153
01:14:27,329 --> 01:14:29,297
吃嘛,你得吃东西
Eat somethin', you gotta eat somethin'.

1154
01:14:31,466 --> 01:14:33,934
你不能不吃东西,吃块牛排
You can't go without eatin'. Eat a steak.

1155
01:14:34,035 --> 01:14:36,936
嚼一嚼再吐出来 体重不会在明天增加的
You chew it, you spit it out, you'll still make the weight tomorrow.

1156
01:14:37,639 --> 01:14:39,106
你在担心这个吗?
You're worried about that?

1157
01:14:41,309 --> 01:14:43,607
我点一块牛排 你想吃的话就可以吃
I'll order a steak. At least if you want it, it's here.

1158
01:14:43,712 --> 01:14:45,612
不想吃就把它处理掉
You don't want it, do whatever you want with it.

1159
01:14:45,714 --> 01:14:48,182
-点啊 -维琪,你要什么?
- Go ahead. - Vickie, what do you want?

1160
01:14:48,884 --> 01:14:50,715
帮我点一块蛋糕
Order me a piece of cake.

1161
01:14:50,819 --> 01:14:52,719
你只想吃一块蛋糕?
That's all you want is a piece of cake?

1162
01:14:52,821 --> 01:14:56,450
怎么不点起司汉堡和薯条? 对你的身体比较好
Why don't you get a cheeseburger, French fries? It's better for you.

1163
01:14:56,558 --> 01:14:58,549
-比较像一顿饭嘛 -好,可以
- It's like a whole meal. - Yeah, that's good.

1164
01:14:58,660 --> 01:15:00,127
可以,帮我点一份
That's good, order me one of those.

1165
01:15:00,228 --> 01:15:02,162
等一下,你想吃什么?
Wait a minute, what do you want to eat?

1166
01:15:02,264 --> 01:15:04,494
你什么时候开始听别人的了?
Since when did you order one of those?

1167
01:15:05,267 --> 01:15:06,996
-那是我想吃的 -这是自由国家
- That's what I want. - It's a free country.

1168
01:15:07,102 --> 01:15:09,229
你点你想吃的,不要让别人左右你
You order what you want. Don't let nobody influence you.

1169
01:15:09,337 --> 01:15:11,464
我没有管她吃什么,我只是提议
I'm not tellin' her what to eat, I was just suggesting.

1170
01:15:11,573 --> 01:15:13,507
你干嘛管她该点什么?
What are you tellin' her what to ask for?

1171
01:15:13,608 --> 01:15:16,736
我没有管她... 我根本不鸟她吃什么
I'm not tellin' her... personally, I don't give a fuck what she eats.

1172
01:15:16,878 --> 01:15:19,506
你干嘛跟她说那些?
What were you tellin' her that for?

1173
01:15:19,581 --> 01:15:21,481
帮我点个起司汉堡
Order me a cheeseburger.

1174
01:15:24,452 --> 01:15:27,046
帮她点个起司汉堡就好
Just order her a cheeseburger, that's all.

1175
01:15:28,256 --> 01:15:29,484
搞什么?
What the f?

1176
01:15:29,591 --> 01:15:32,685
你们怎么弄这么久? 这要花多久时间?
What are you guys doin' so long? How long does this thing take to do?

1177
01:15:32,794 --> 01:15:33,761
四十秒
Forty seconds.

1178
01:15:33,862 --> 01:15:36,422
四十秒不行,得在三十秒内弄完
Forty seconds is no good. You gotta do it in 30 seconds.

1179
01:15:36,531 --> 01:15:38,658
缝合伤口的时间就只有这么多
If we gotta stitch him up, that's how much time.

1180
01:15:43,138 --> 01:15:44,264
你醒了吗?
Ya up?

1181
01:15:44,806 --> 01:15:47,274
-干嘛? -有人来找你
- What? - Somebody's here to see ya.

1182
01:15:48,410 --> 01:15:49,775
-嘿,杰克 -嘿,汤米,你好吗?
- Hey, Jack. - Hey, Tommy, how you doin'?

1183
01:15:49,878 --> 01:15:51,175
你好吗?
How are you?

1184
01:15:56,818 --> 01:15:58,615
和查理打个招呼,查理!
Say hello to Charlie. Charlie!

1185
01:15:58,720 --> 01:16:01,348
-杰克,你好吗?祝你好运 -查理,真高兴看到你
- Jake, how are ya? Lots of luck. - Hello, Charlie, good to see you.

1186
01:16:01,890 --> 01:16:03,187
谢谢
Thank you.

1187
01:16:04,326 --> 01:16:07,261
-你的心情如何? -心情很好,谢谢
- How you feeling? - I'm feelin' all right, thank you.

1188
01:16:07,362 --> 01:16:10,456
-心情还好吧? -我会保持愉快心情
- Are you feeling good? - I feel as good as I'm gonna feel.

1189
01:16:10,565 --> 01:16:13,033
我得先上场比赛 然后就知道有什么心情了
I gotta get in there and fight, then I'll know how I'm gonna feel.

1190
01:16:13,134 --> 01:16:16,228
好,我们只是来祝你好运
All right. We just come by to wish you luck and all that.

1191
01:16:16,338 --> 01:16:17,805
-谢谢 -你需要什么吗?
- Thanks. - You need anything?

1192
01:16:17,906 --> 01:16:19,271
-没有 -你确定?
- No. - You sure, nothing?

1193
01:16:19,374 --> 01:16:20,341
不用,汤米,谢谢
No, thank you, Tommy.

1194
01:16:20,442 --> 01:16:22,501
好吧,保重,祝你好运
All right. Take care, good luck.

1195
01:16:22,611 --> 01:16:24,306
-上帝保佑 -好,汤米,谢谢
- God bless ya. - All right, thank you.

1196
01:16:24,412 --> 01:16:26,710
-你没问题的 -是啊,我没问题
- You'll be all right. - Yeah, I'll be all right.

1197
01:16:27,515 --> 01:16:28,777
大家待会见了
See you later, everybody.

1198
01:16:28,884 --> 01:16:30,749
-维琪,再见 -汤米,等一下
- Vickie, good-bye. - Tommy, wait.

1199
01:16:30,852 --> 01:16:33,320
我想告诉你 我们很感激你来看我们
We really appreciate your comin', I want you to know that.

1200
01:16:33,421 --> 01:16:35,582
你真有心,谢谢了
It was really nice of you. I appreciate it.

1201
01:16:35,690 --> 01:16:38,557
-好了,乔伊,别客气 -这种时候对他非常重要
- Come on, Joey, anytime. - A time like this is very important to him.

1202
01:16:38,660 --> 01:16:40,958
-别客气 -我只是想跟你说再见
- Anytime. - I just wanted to say good-bye.

1203
01:16:41,062 --> 01:16:43,895
再见,甜心 好好照顾那家伙好吗?
So long, honey. I want you to take good care of that guy, all right?

1204
01:16:43,999 --> 01:16:46,263
-我会照顾他 -乔伊,有任何状况
- I'll take care of him. - Joey, any little thing,

1205
01:16:46,368 --> 01:16:49,098
就打电话给我 就连他紧张一下也打电话来
I want you to call me. He's very nervous. Ba-boom, call.

1206
01:16:49,204 --> 01:16:50,193
再见,甜心
Good-bye, honey.

1207
01:16:51,473 --> 01:16:53,839
你看看那张脸蛋,真美啊
Would you look at that face? What a face.

1208
01:16:53,942 --> 01:16:55,603
真令人不敢相信
Can you believe that girl?

1209
01:16:55,710 --> 01:16:58,042
看看这个美女,永远那么美
Look at that beauty. Just as beautiful as ever.

1210
01:16:58,146 --> 01:17:00,341
-注意所有的状况好吗? -再见,汤米
- The least little thing, all right? - Bye-bye, Tommy.

1211
01:17:00,448 --> 01:17:03,906
-大家再见了 -再见,汤米
- So long, everybody. - So long, Tommy.

1212
01:17:13,495 --> 01:17:15,292
嘿!过来
Hey! Come here.

1213
01:17:16,064 --> 01:17:17,361
过来一下
Come here a minute.

1214
01:17:24,773 --> 01:17:26,400
刚才是怎么回事?
What was all that about?

1215
01:17:27,108 --> 01:17:28,132
什么?
All what?

1216
01:17:28,243 --> 01:17:30,006
你知道我在说什么? 那是怎么回事?
You know what I'm talkin' about. What was that all about?

1217
01:17:31,780 --> 01:17:34,749
-和他那样 -没什么,我只是道再见
- With him. - Nothin', I just said good-bye.

1218
01:17:34,849 --> 01:17:36,942
你突然间对他这么友善?
All of a sudden you're so friendly with him?

1219
01:17:37,052 --> 01:17:38,747
-我只是说声再见 -不是那样做
- I just said good-bye. - You don't do that.

1220
01:17:38,853 --> 01:17:41,219
你说哈跟再见就好 听到了没?
You say hello, you say good-bye, that's all, ya hear?

1221
01:17:41,323 --> 01:17:42,790
-听到了 -嘿!
- I hear. - Hey!

1222
01:17:43,391 --> 01:17:46,019
你听到我的话没? 你要尊重我
You hear what I said? You don't ever have any disrespect for me.

1223
01:17:46,127 --> 01:17:47,754
你听到我的话没?
You hear what I said?

1224
01:17:49,331 --> 01:17:52,129
-听到了 -好,给我进去
- Yeah, I hear. - All right. Go in there.

1225
01:17:53,034 --> 01:17:55,002
-过来 -你别那样好不好?
- Come here. - Why don't you stop that?

1226
01:17:55,103 --> 01:17:56,730
你给我闭嘴!闭嘴!
Shut up, you! Shut up!

1227
01:17:56,838 --> 01:17:59,306
闭嘴!待会再来跟你算帐!
Shut up! I'll fuckin' take care of you later!

1228
01:17:59,374 --> 01:18:00,500
闭嘴!
Shut up!

1229
01:18:08,917 --> 01:18:11,385
你们两个让我想吐
Disgusted with the two of youse.

1230
01:18:15,924 --> 01:18:17,323
待会再跟你们算帐
Get to youse later.

1231
01:18:22,464 --> 01:18:24,932
我是老大,我是老大...
I'm the boss, I'm the boss...

1232
01:18:27,469 --> 01:18:29,266
用力打啊,快点!
Hit the fuckin' thing, come on!

1233
01:18:31,306 --> 01:18:32,603
好了,走吧
All right, let's go.

1234
01:19:03,505 --> 01:19:05,132
祝你好运,杰克!
Good luck, Jake!

1235
01:19:18,019 --> 01:19:19,987
杰克

1236
01:19:44,813 --> 01:19:49,546
中量级世界冠军赛 共有十五局赛
For the Middleweight Championship of the World, 15 rounds.

1237
01:19:49,651 --> 01:19:53,212
一边是非常杰出的挑战者
In this corner, the very worthy challenger,

1238
01:19:53,321 --> 01:19:56,757
体重一百五十八又四分一磅
weighing in at 1581/4 pounds,

1239
01:19:56,858 --> 01:20:01,158
布朗克斯公牛 杰克拉莫塔!
the Bronx Bull, Jake La Motta!

1240
01:20:07,735 --> 01:20:09,635
握个手,铃响就开始比赛
Shake hands, come out fighting at the bell.

1241
01:20:09,737 --> 01:20:11,671
拉莫塔对中量级冠军马赛瑟登 底特律1949年

1242
01:20:29,591 --> 01:20:31,422
第三局 布里格斯体育场

1243
01:20:31,526 --> 01:20:32,857
宰了他!
Kill him!

1244
01:20:36,731 --> 01:20:38,631
第七局 布里格斯体育场

1245
01:20:38,733 --> 01:20:40,291
压力,给他压力!
Pressure, pressure, pressure!

1246
01:20:41,836 --> 01:20:43,201
第九局 布里格斯体育场

1247
01:20:51,980 --> 01:20:55,438
把他解决掉 他已经神智不清了,你稳赢
Now finish him off. He's all stupiada, you got him.

1248
01:20:55,984 --> 01:20:57,110
加油,杰克!
Come on, Jake!

1249
01:20:58,820 --> 01:21:01,288
给他一拳,他会立刻倒地的
Blow on him, he'll fuckin' fall right over for ya.

1250
01:21:01,356 --> 01:21:04,018
你看他,你还好吧?
Look at him. Do you feel all right?

1251
01:21:06,828 --> 01:21:08,659
-不行啦? -不能继续了?
- No way, huh? - Can't continue?

1252
01:21:09,330 --> 01:21:12,128
委员?来一下,我要停止比赛
Hey, Commissioner? Come on in, I'm gonna stop the fight.

1253
01:21:12,233 --> 01:21:13,700
你成功了,杰克!
Yeah, you did it, Jake!

1254
01:21:25,780 --> 01:21:28,908
各位女士先生请注意
Ladies and gentlemen, may I have your attention, please?

1255
01:21:29,117 --> 01:21:33,520
瑟登无法继续比赛 裁判宣布停赛
Cerdan, unable to continue, the referee stops the fight.

1256
01:21:33,621 --> 01:21:35,851
技术性击倒的胜利者
And the winner by a technical knockout

1257
01:21:35,957 --> 01:21:37,356
在第十局出现
in the tenth round,

1258
01:21:37,458 --> 01:21:40,222
新的中量级世界冠军
and the new Middleweight Champion of the World,

1259
01:21:40,461 --> 01:21:44,090
布朗克斯公牛 杰克拉莫塔!
the Bronx Bull, Jake La Motta!

1260
01:21:47,535 --> 01:21:50,663
杰克!杰克!杰克!杰克!
Jake! Jake! Jake! Jake!

1261
01:22:06,321 --> 01:22:08,016
佩尔汉大道 纽约1950年

1262
01:22:08,122 --> 01:22:11,285
不要摇它 不要那样摇它,我告诉你
Don't shake that. Don't shake it like that, I'm tellin' ya.

1263
01:22:11,392 --> 01:22:13,087
那是最糟的做法
It's the worst thing you could do.

1264
01:22:18,499 --> 01:22:19,796
哦,你在家
Oh, you're home.

1265
01:22:20,835 --> 01:22:23,235
-嗨,维琪 -嗨,乔
- Hi, Vick. - Hi, Joe.

1266
01:22:26,007 --> 01:22:28,407
-哈 -嗨,你去哪了?
- Hello. - Hi. Where were ya?

1267
01:22:28,509 --> 01:22:31,410
出去了,怎么回事?
I went out. What's the matter?

1268
01:22:31,512 --> 01:22:32,979
电视不能看
Television won't work.

1269
01:22:33,848 --> 01:22:35,338
你去哪里?
Where'd you go?

1270
01:22:35,450 --> 01:22:39,750
出去,去血拼,去我妹那儿嘛
Went out, went shoppin'. Went to my sister's. You know.

1271
01:22:51,132 --> 01:22:54,659
你是怎么搞的? 干嘛亲她的嘴?
What's the matter with you? What's with this kissin' on the mouth?

1272
01:22:54,769 --> 01:22:56,828
我只是打个招呼 我不能亲我的大嫂吗?
I just said hello. Can't I kiss my sister-in-law?

1273
01:22:56,938 --> 01:22:58,462
亲脸颊还不够吗?
Isn't the cheek good enough for you?

1274
01:22:58,573 --> 01:22:59,540
别这样好吗?
Come on, huh?

1275
01:22:59,641 --> 01:23:01,199
我就不会像你亲她那样 亲老妈的嘴
I don't even kiss Mom on the mouth the way you kiss her.

1276
01:23:01,309 --> 01:23:02,901
突然间,你成了大情圣
All of a sudden, you're like a Romeo.

1277
01:23:03,011 --> 01:23:04,945
你本来就不该亲妈妈的嘴
You're not supposed to kiss your mother on the mouth.

1278
01:23:05,046 --> 01:23:06,673
我就是这个意思
That's what I'm talkin' about.

1279
01:23:11,552 --> 01:23:13,918
-怎么样? -好像有东西了
- How's that? - That looks like somethin'.

1280
01:23:17,992 --> 01:23:21,052
后退点,你的肚子挡到看不到
